						<div class="col-1"></div>
						<div class="col-7">
							<div class="quote">Since 2021, the Climate Change and Urban Environment Community of Practice has hosted 16 sessions, bringing more than 400 colleagues together to discuss themes, events and initiatives like urban heat, urban biodiversity, IPCC reports, COPs, SURGe and I4C. Many of these sessions have been achieved in collaboration with other Communities of Practice and external partners like UNDP. Through one of the discussions, we gathered nature-based solutions case studies in more than 30 cities  across the agency</div>
